import React from 'react'

import {Container, Spacer, Button,ButtonContainer} from './BottomBar.styles'

/* 
    TODO: Render out buttons so they work with paginated results
          There should be no more then 4 buttons displayed.
          If there are more then 4 pages, then the last button should show
          the final page number.
          
          If there are there are less then 4 pages only 
*/


const BottomBar = () => {
    return(
        <Container>
            <ButtonContainer>
                <Button isEnd> {"< Prev"}</Button>
                <Button>1</Button>
                <Button isActive>2</Button>
                <Button>3</Button>
                <Spacer>...</Spacer>
                <Button>27</Button>
                <Button isEnd>{"Next >"}</Button>
            </ButtonContainer>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default BottomBar
